title: Tory Lanez Interview and more
itunes:title: Tory Lanez Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Tory Lanez stop by and we went right into Tory Lanez hair, in which he got a PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) surgery. He also spoke about his new album, being friends with Drake, diss tracks and more. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to culturally clueless Hollywood who tried to make Julia Roberts play the role of Harriet Tubman and Angela helped some listeners with "Ask Yee".
